@startuml
title 5. Create Release Tag (Simplified)
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor Student as S
participant "GitWizard" as W

S -> W : Option 5

W -> S : "Available tags:\n  R1 - UI Prototype\n  R2 - Implementation + Tests\n  R3 - Documentation"

S -> W : R2

W -> S : "Create tag R2? (y/n)"
S -> W : y
W -> W : git tag -a R2\ngit push origin R2

W -> S : "Release tag R2\ncreated and pushed!"

note right of S
  Tag is visible on GitHub.
  Instructors evaluate this
  exact version.
end note
@enduml
